    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical attention and cosmetic restoration. The engine currently struggles to start and exhibits a noticeable knock, while the transmission shifts roughly between gears. The exterior shows several large dents, peeling clear coat, and visible rust on the rocker panels. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with several tears, and the electronic systems, including the radio and air conditioning, are currently non-functional. This is a project car best suited for a mechanic or someone looking for a complete rebuild.",
